                <summary>The paper reports that the Augusta (Stribling) Springs has a large number
                    of visitors this season. "It is a beautiful, pleasant and healthy Summer
                    retreat--is kept in the best style--has a variety of mineral waters and is fast
                    winning its way in popular esteem."</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
